001package com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.types.WalletMessage;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004
005import java.util.Arrays;
006import java.util.function.Predicate;
007
008public enum WalletMessageType {
009    PAIRING_PAYLOAD("pairingPayload"),
010    PAIRING_EVENT("pairingEvent"),
011    CREDENTIAL_EVENT("credentialEvent"),
012    UNKNOWN("unknown");
013
014    private final String rawValue;
015
016    WalletMessageType(@NonNull final String rawValue) {
017        this.rawValue = rawValue;
018    }
019
020    public String getRawValue() {
021        return rawValue;
022    }
023
024    public static WalletMessageType fromRawValue(String message) {
025     return Arrays.stream(WalletMessageType.values()).filter(new Predicate<WalletMessageType>() {
026            @Override
027            public boolean test(WalletMessageType walletMessageType) {
028                return walletMessageType.getRawValue().equals(message);
029            }
030        }).findFirst().orElse(null);
031    }
032
033}
034
